  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compared short- and long-time action observation training (AOT) in terms of grip strength,
      the Jebsen Taylor Hand Function Test (JTHF), the Quality of Upper Extremities Skills Test
      (QUEST), and the ABILHAND-Kids test.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
